      QA('What are the three types of conditional sentences? Give examples.',
          'Type 1 (real): If it rains, the match will be cancelled. Type 2 (unreal present): If I were a bird, I would fly. Type 3 (unreal past): If he had studied, he would have passed.'),
      QA('Add a question tag: "She has completed the project, ___?"',
